title: ROBOS: GIBBERISH VOCALIZATIONS, P2
description: Robotic and High-Tech Alien Voices Soundpack for Sci-Fi Games
longDescription:
Listen to the watermarked demo of some of the sounds:

CLICK HERE

 

“Created by us using industry-leading sound design techniques, we introduce “ROBOS: GIBBERISH VOCALIZATIONS, P2,” a versatile audio asset pack featuring a collection of unique robotic gibberish vocalizations from clear to nasty tonalities, perfect for adding character and personality to your game projects. With 10 distinct types of tonalities, each organized into separate folders, this pack offers a wide range of sounds to suit various in-game scenarios.”


Key Features:


15 Types of Tonalities: Each folder contains a different set of robotic gibberish vocalizations, providing a diverse array of sounds to choose from.

Emotions: There are sounds in both flat as well as aggressive expressions.

High-Quality Audio: All sound effects are recorded and processed in high quality to ensure clarity and impact.

Versatile Use Cases: Suitable for various game genres, including sci-fi, fantasy, adventure, and more.
